  "content": {
    "prompt": "<div><div class=\"stimulus_reference\"><div class=\"passage\"><div class=\"prose style:1\"><div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"The figure shows a top view of a disk with its center indicated.&nbsp;Two points on the disk are labeled “Person 1” and “Person 2.” Person 2 is at the edge of the disk to the left of center, and Person 1 is between the center and Person 2.\" src=\"/images/6f6a5cfa181133183bcad2d3f82d139e.svg\"></div></div></div></div></div><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">Two people are sitting on a large metal disk at a park. Person <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"1\"><math alttext=\"1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>1</mn></math></span></span> is halfway between the center and the edge, while Person <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2\"><math alttext=\"2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>2</mn></math></span></span> is at the edge of the disk, as shown. The disk accelerates from rest until it reaches an angular velocity of <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"omega sub f\"><math alttext=\"omega sub f\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><msub><mi>ω</mi><mi>f</mi></msub></mstyle></math></span></span>. Which of the following correctly compares the angular acceleration, <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"alpha\"><math alttext=\"alpha\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>α</mi></math></span></span>, and the tangential acceleration, <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"a\"><math alttext=\"a\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>a</mi></math></span></span>, of Person <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"1\"><math alttext=\"1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>1</mn></math></span></span> and Person <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2\"><math alttext=\"2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>2</mn></math></span></span>?</p><div class=\"table_wrapper\"><table class=\"tgroup align:center cols:3 colsep:0 frame:none rowsep:0\"><colgroup><col class=\"colspec colname:col1 colnum:1 colsep:1\"><col class=\"colspec colname:col2 colnum:2 colwidth:95\"><col class=\"colspec colname:col3 colnum:3 colwidth:95\"></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\"><tr class=\"row rowsep:1\"><th class=\"entry colname:col1\"></th><th class=\"entry colname:col2\">Angular</th><th class=\"entry colname:col3\">Tangential</th></tr></thead><tbody class=\"tbody valign:middle\"><tr class=\"row\"><td class=\"entry colname:col1\">A</td><td class=\"entry colname:col2\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"alpha sub 1 equals alpha sub 2\"><math alttext=\"alpha sub 1 equals alpha sub 2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><msub><mi>α</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>α</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mstyle></math></span></span></td><td class=\"entry colname:col3\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"a sub 1 equals a sub 2\"><math alttext=\"a sub 1 equals a sub 2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mstyle></math></span></span></td></tr><tr class=\"row\"><td class=\"entry colname:col1\">B</td><td class=\"entry colname:col2\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"alpha sub 1 equals alpha sub 2\"><math alttext=\"alpha sub 1 equals alpha sub 2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><msub><mi>α</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>α</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mstyle></math></span></span></td><td class=\"entry colname:col3\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"a sub 1 is less than a sub 2\"><math alttext=\"a sub 1 is less than a sub 2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>&lt;</mo><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></math></span></span></td></tr><tr class=\"row\"><td class=\"entry colname:col1\">C</